snippet.title: Reality Bites: Troy and Lelaina reunite
snippet.description:
Troy (Ethan Hawke) sings a song for Lelaina (Winona Ryder) in a bar. She immediately runs away. Michael (Ben Stiller) and Troy try to follow her outside but she is already gone.
